          <div
            style="display:inline-block;background:rgba(201,150,62,.2);border:1px solid rgba(201,150,62,.4);color:var(--gold-light);font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:50px;margin-bottom:14px;">
            MODEL 1</div>
          <h1
            style="font-family:&#39;Playfair Display&#39;,serif;font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,64px);font-weight:900;color:#fff;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:12px;">
            Supported Farming<br>with <span style="color:var(--gold-light);">Shared Income</span></h1>
          <p style="font-size:17px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);line-height:1.72;margin-bottom:34px;max-width:460px;">We
            provide everything you need. You focus on farming. Together we grow — and share the outcome fairly.</p>
          <div class="cta-btns"><button class="btn btn-gold" onclick="showPage(&#39;contact&#39;)">Partner With
              Us</button><button class="btn btn-outline">Learn How It Works</button></div>
        </div>
        <div class="model-steps-card">
          <div class="model-steps-label">HOW IT WORKS</div>
          <div class="model-step">
            <div class="model-step-num">1</div>
            <div class="model-step-text">We provide land with strong, healthy soil</div>
          </div>
          <div class="model-step">
            <div class="model-step-num">2</div>
            <div class="model-step-text">We provide seeds, tools, and farming apps</div>
          </div>
          <div class="model-step">
            <div class="model-step-num">3</div>
            <div class="model-step-text">We guide you throughout the crop cycle</div>
          </div>
