          <div>
            <div class="section-tag">OUR STORY</div>
            <h2 class="section-heading white">Rooted in Purpose,<br>Grown with Care</h2>
            <p class="section-sub white" style="margin-top:14px;">We cultivate on 40 acres of certified organic land
              near Chennai. No synthetic fertilizers. Just patient farming, living soil, and the kind of nourishment
              your grandparents knew.</p>
            <div class="farmer-features" style="margin-top:22px;">
              <div class="farmer-feature">
                <div class="farmer-feature-icon">🌍</div>
                <div>
                  <div class="farmer-feature-title">Living Fertile Soil</div>
                  <div class="farmer-feature-desc">We build soil health over years using natural compost and microbial
                    communities — never synthetic inputs.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="farmer-feature">
                <div class="farmer-feature-icon">💧</div>
                <div>
                  <div class="farmer-feature-title">Pure Clean Water</div>
                  <div class="farmer-feature-desc">Irrigation from tested groundwater springs, free from agricultural
                    contamination.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="farmer-feature">
                <div class="farmer-feature-icon">🌱</div>
                <div>
                  <div class="farmer-feature-title">Native Non-GMO Seeds</div>
                  <div class="farmer-feature-desc">Traditional Indian varieties selected for climate resilience and
                    nutritional density.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="farmer-feature">
                <div class="farmer-feature-icon">🔬</div>
                <div>
                  <div class="farmer-feature-title">Lab-Certified Every Batch</div>
                  <div class="farmer-feature-desc">Every harvest tested for 200+ pesticide residues, heavy metals, and
                    microbial safety.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="csa-story-img"><img src="https://chediwebsite.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/images/land-morning.jpg"
              alt="Organic farm" loading="lazy"></div>
        </div>
